Class RTCoupledHIOA_Descriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.architectures.CoupledModelDescriptor
      • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.architectures.CoupledHIOA_Descriptor

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelDescriptorI, java.io.Serializable

    public class RTCoupledHIOA_Descriptor
extends CoupledHIOA_Descriptor
    The class RTCoupledHIOA_Descriptor describes real time coupled HIOA in model architectures.

    Description

    The need for this class is to cope with the case when a coupled model is created with a real time atomic simulation engine which acceleration factor must be initialised.

    Invariant

     invariant      true

    Created on : 2020-11-30

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
    See Also:
    Serialized Form

        engineCreationMode - creation mode for the simulation engine.
        importedVars - map from variables imported by this coupled HIOA and the submodels consuming them.
        reexportedVars - map from variables exported by this coupled HIOA and the submodels producing them.
        bindings - map between variables exported by submodels to ones imported by others.
